{
  "text": "This finding is corroborated by the earlier research in AIED, which found human awareness as an essential component in building educational AI and calls for a greater need to design student-centered and education-sensitive AI-embedded systems that understands students' diverse characteristics within the educational domain so that it fits right into our existing educational practice and processes (Lee et al., 2023).",
